{
  "id": "adv_main_02_05_01",
  "title": "東京編1章21話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_unrest-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob1",
      "speakerName": "アナウンサー",
      "speakerNameEn": "Announcer",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_01-mannouncer001.m4a",
      "text": "芸能事務所・バンプロダクション社長",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Talent Agency Van Productions’ Company President‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob1",
      "speakerName": "アナウンサー",
      "speakerNameEn": "Announcer",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "朝倉恭一氏が横領の容疑で、逮捕されました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kyoichi Asakura‚ has been arrested on suspicion of embezzlement.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.966666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob1",
      "speakerName": "アナウンサー",
      "speakerNameEn": "Announcer",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_01-mannouncer002.m4a",
      "text": "関係者の話では",
      "translations": {
        "en": "According to sources‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.033333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob1",
      "speakerName": "アナウンサー",
      "speakerNameEn": "Announcer",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "朝倉容疑者は容疑を否認しており――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Asakura denies the charges…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_01-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "うちは、ウソやと思う\n誤認逮捕ちゃうかな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t think it’s true.\nThey must have the wrong person.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.633333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_01-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうだよ！　こんなの何かの間違いだよ！\n瑠依ちゃん、きっとすぐに疑いは晴れるよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Th-that’s right! This has to be some kind of mistake!\nRui-chan‚ I’m sure his name will be cleared!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.533333333333335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_01-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "……え、ええ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "R-right…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ここにもマスコミが来るかもしれないし\n長居は出来ない。みんな、私物を取ったら寮に向かおう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The media may show up here‚ too. We can’t stick around.\nOnce everyone gathers their things‚ let’s head to the dorm.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.26666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_01-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん\nライブ会場の他の子らは、このこともう知ってんの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san!\nDo the girls at the festival know about this yet?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.233333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "橋本さんに連絡して事情は伝えてあるよ\nフェスが終わったらすぐ戻ってくる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve contacted Hashimoto-san‚ and she’s delivered the news.\nThey’ll leave right after the festival.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.166666666666664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_01-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "私達がバンプロから星見プロに移籍したばっかりだから\nみんなの所にもマスコミの人が来るのかな……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’ve just transferred here from Van Productions.\nI wonder if the media will come after everyone here as well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_01-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "ない、とは言い切れんなぁ\nあの人らは特ダネ欲しさでやっきになってるやろし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s not implausible.\nThose jackals will do anything for a scoop.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.733333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_01-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "……すみません\n星見プロにご迷惑を……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Sorry.\nWe’ve put Hoshimi Productions in a tight spot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.93333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "みんなは、TRINITYAiLEは何も悪くない\nそれにアイドルを守るのは事務所として当然だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You three did nothing wrong.\nBesides‚ it’s our job as an agency to protect our idols.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.86666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_achieve-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 73.13333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_01-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.13333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_01-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ頼りになるなぁ\n瑠依ちゃん、うちらここに来て正解やったね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Heheh. You’re so dependable.\nRui-chan‚ we made the right decision coming here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_01-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "え、ええ、ありがとうございます\n{user}さん、私は……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-yeah. Thank you.\n{user}-san‚ I…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_01-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "本当のことを知りたいです\n……いえ、知らなければいけないんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to know the truth.\nNo. I have to know the truth.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.13333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_01-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "私は、あの人の、娘ですから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because… I’m his daughter.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな。でも今、朝倉さんは警察にいる\nしばらくは会えないと思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re right. But he’s with the police right now.\nI don’t think you’ll be able to see him for a while.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_01-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "私、姫野さんに会いに行きます\nあの人ならきっと真実を知っているはずです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m going to go meet with Himeno-san.\nIf anyone knows the truth‚ it’s her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_01-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "会う？　直接会うつもりなん？\nバンプロはマスコミが何十人と詰めかけてるで？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Meet with her? You mean in person?\nVan Productions is currently swarmed by reporters‚ you know?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.13333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_01-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "電話もメッセも反応がないんだもの！\nもう直接会うしか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But she won’t answer my calls or texts!\nI have to meet her in person.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1900.0000000000057,
          "startTime": 121.93333333333334
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_01-stm001.m4a",
      "text": "た、大変です、{user}さん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "O-oh dear‚ {user}-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_stm-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 124.66666666666669
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "おかえり。早かったね、橋本さん\nみんなは大丈夫？　マスコミに追われなかった？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Welcome back‚ Hashimoto-san. You got back here fast.\nIs everyone okay? Were they hounded by the paparazzi?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_01-stm002.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　みなさんは無事に\nシェアハウスに連れて行きました！　ご安心を！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They’re fine! They’re all safe\nat the share-house right now! Rest at ease!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.76666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_01-stm003.m4a",
      "text": "マスコミっぽい方はちらほらいましたけど\n隙を見て――って、そうじゃなくて！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I did see some paparazzi-ish people about‚\nbut I found my opening and… wait‚ forget about that!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_01-stm004.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんにお客様なんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ you have a visitor!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.66666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "来客？　さすがに今はちょっと\n後日、俺から連絡するって伝えてもらえないかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A visitor? Now’s a really bad time.\nCan you tell them I’ll call in a few days?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_01-stm005.m4a",
      "text": "そんなこと出来ません！　あの方にそんな無体なこと\n私が言える訳ないじゃないですか！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ we can’t do that! I could never be so rude\nto such an esteemed person!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
